    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "JOSEPH PERRY, GRAND BLANC, MICHIGAN - COMPLAINANT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "MISCELLANEOUS - INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "(NATIONAL INTELLIGENCE)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "ReBulet to Office of Special Investigations, Air Force, dated",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "4/6/60.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "On Saturday, 4/9/60, Agents of the Flint, Mich., Resident Agency",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "attempted to contact JOSEPH PERRY at his home, 3079 Edward St.,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Grand Blanc, Mich., with negative results.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "On 4/9/60 he was located telephonically at approximately 6:30 P.M.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "He advised that he would not be available for interview that night",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "or over the weekend; therefore, he was advised that his letter to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "the White House had been referred to the FBI by the Dept. of Justice,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "and we desired to acknowledge the letter and to see him personally.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Mr. PERRY advised that he would arrange to contact the Agents at the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "earliest possible date.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "On 4/11/60 appointment was made to see PERRY on 4/12/60, at which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "time Bureau's complete instructions will be complied with.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
